data.description: MOVE IN READY!!! 4/2 B/B or 3/2 B/B with Office or Formal Dining Room. Stone counters, rich wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, large windows, sliding glass doors with a large backyard with garden-landscaped lined fence. This gorgeous home with an room facing the front garden, is located inside the desirable cypress neighborhood with limited space to build left. The perfect location with Publix 3 streets away, 1st Golf Course w/clubhouse is 2 streets away, 2nd Golf Course is 4 streets away, the beach and intracoastal can be biked to.. Schools, churches, city parks and recreation centers are all within a few miles. Maximize the best of what Palm Coast, Florida has to offer living so close to the city and still feel nature surrounding you.
